<mvc:View controllerName="iot.timetracking-worklist.controller.CreateEntity" 
  xmlns="sap.m" 
  xmlns:form="sap.ui.layout.form" 
  xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc">
  <Page showHeader="false" floatingFooter="true">
    <form:SimpleForm  editable="true">
      <!-- <Label labelFor="nameInput" text="{/##Employees/name@com.sap.vocabularies.Common.v1.Label}"/> -->
      <Label labelFor="nameInput" text="Name"/>
      <Input id="labelInput" value="{viewModel>/newEntity/name}"/>
    </form:SimpleForm>
    <footer>
      <Toolbar>
        <ToolbarSpacer/>
        <Button text="Speichern" press="onPressSave" type="Emphasized"/>
        <Button text="Abbrechen" press="onPressCancel"/>
      </Toolbar>
    </footer>
  </Page>
</mvc:View>